comments: McLemore (POR) is already in Stewart's (DET) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
McLemore (POR) is already in Bey's (DET) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Stewart (DET) legally contests Williams' (POR) jump shot attempt.
Hayes (DET) and Watford (POR) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Stewart (DET) is firming up over his right leg in Dunn's (POR) path and he absorbs the contact to his upper body.
Stewart (DET) is already in Dunn's (POR) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Winslow (POR) and Cunningham (DET) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Bagley III (DET) is moving alongside Williams' (POR) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Stewart (DET) hooks Winslow (DET) at the start of his drive. This foul was upgraded to a Flagrant Foul Penalty I following postgame review.
Hayes (DET) places his hand momentarily on Williams' (POR) side and immediately removes his hand as Williams moves to receive the ball.
Williams (POR) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Williams (POR) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot, which he maintains after his gather.
Bagley III (DET) and Watford (POR) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Watford back taps the ball.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Williams (POR).
Watford (POR) legally contests Livers' (DET) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on McLemore (POR).
